item.title: About Me
item.description: My name is Andy, how may I take your order? I am a full-stack engineer, born in raised in Los Angeles and residing in Seattle. I love gorging myself on everything from sushi to sourdough, trying my hand at different sports (earlier this year was badminton and bouldering, but I’ve since gotten back on the saddle and started cycling again), and cheering on my hometown Los Angeles Dodgers. After getting my degree in Political Economy from UC Berkeley in 2017, I moved up to Seattle and (perhaps inevitably) was sucked into the tech bubble.
